requests.name: Users SetPlayerBranding

requests.name: Users SetProfile

requests.name: Videos AddClosedCaptioning
requests.description: Add new closed captioning file for a specific video. All uploaded closed captioning files are enabled by default. The first uploaded file is default for a video.

queryParams.description: The language of the file (Max Characters: 50)

requests.name: Videos Comments Get
requests.description: Get comments for a video. If logged in and querying comments for own video – all comments with any moderation status will be returned. If quering comments as logged out or for not owned video – only approved comments will be returned if the video itself is public.

queryParams.description: comment parent ID if you want to get the responses to that particular comment
